# The Problem Solving Process With Data

<div style="background-color: #F7F8FA; border-radius: 40px; color: #000000; width: 95%; padding: 10px 10px 10px 10px;"> <p style="line-height: 1.5; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px;">The <b>Problem Solving Process</b> is a tool for structured problem solving that is woven throughout the entire course to promote student growth and development. The Data and Society unit uses the problem solving process with data. 
</p></div>
